## 6. Project Timeline & Milestones

### 6.1 High-Level Project Phases
**Phase 1: Foundation (Weeks 1-4)**
- Requirements finalization and system architecture
- Database schema design and implementation
- Development environment setup
- **Milestone**: Technical foundation established

**Phase 2: Core Development (Weeks 5-10)**
- API development and authentication system
- AI model integration and testing
- Database integration and data management
- **Milestone**: Core functionality operational

**Phase 3: Advanced Features (Weeks 11-14)**
- Premium feature development
- Analytics and reporting capabilities
- Performance optimization
- **Milestone**: Feature-complete system

**Phase 4: Testing & Deployment (Weeks 15-18)**
- Comprehensive testing and bug fixes
- Production deployment and monitoring
- User acceptance testing
- **Milestone**: Production-ready system launched

### 6.2 Critical Path Dependencies
1. Database schema completion → Core API development
2. Authentication system → Multi-tenant functionality
3. AI model integration → Document processing features
4. Performance testing → Production deployment
5. Security testing → User data handling features

