## 7. Resource Requirements

### 7.1 Human Resources
- **Development Team**: 5 full-time team members for 18 weeks
- **External Resources**: 
  - UI/UX Designer (contract, 4 weeks)
  - Security Consultant (contract, 2 weeks)
  - Cloud Infrastructure Specialist (contract, ongoing)

### 7.2 Technical Resources
**Development Infrastructure:**
- Development environments and IDEs
- Testing frameworks and tools
- Version control system (GitHub)
- Project management tools

**Production Infrastructure:**
- Cloud hosting platform (AWS/Google Cloud/Azure)
- Database hosting (PostgreSQL, MongoDB, Redis)
- Content Delivery Network (CDN)
- Monitoring and analytics tools
- SSL certificates and security tools

### 7.3 Budget Estimate
**Development Phase:**
- Personnel costs: R450,000 (18 weeks × 5 resources)
- Infrastructure costs: R25,000
- Third-party services: R15,000
- Contingency (15%): R73,500
- **Total Budget**: R563,500

