## 8. Risk Management

### 8.1 High-Risk Items
**Technical Risks:**
- **AI Model Performance** (High Impact, Medium Probability)
  - Risk: Summarization quality below user expectations
  - Mitigation: Multiple model testing, fallback options, user feedback loops

- **API Reliability** (High Impact, Low Probability)
  - Risk: OCDS API downtime affecting core functionality
  - Mitigation: Caching strategy, backup data sources, offline mode

- **Scalability Issues** (Medium Impact, Medium Probability)
  - Risk: System performance degradation under load
  - Mitigation: Load testing, auto-scaling infrastructure, performance monitoring

**Business Risks:**
- **Market Adoption** (High Impact, Medium Probability)
  - Risk: Lower than expected user registration and engagement
  - Mitigation: Market research, pilot programs, iterative feature development

- **Competitive Response** (Medium Impact, Low Probability)
  - Risk: Established players launching similar solutions
  - Mitigation: Rapid development, unique value proposition, first-mover advantage

### 8.2 Risk Monitoring
- Weekly risk assessment reviews
- Monthly stakeholder risk reports
- Automated system monitoring and alerts
- User feedback tracking and analysis

---

## 9. Quality Assurance & Compliance

### 9.1 Quality Standards
- **Code Quality**: 80%+ test coverage, peer code reviews, automated testing
- **Security**: OWASP compliance, regular vulnerability assessments
- **Performance**: <2 second response times, 99.5% uptime SLA
- **Usability**: WCAG 2.1 AA compliance, user experience testing

### 9.2 Compliance Requirements
- **Data Privacy**: POPIA (Protection of Personal Information Act) compliance
- **Open Standards**: OCDS (Open Contracting Data Standard) adherence
- **Security**: ISO 27001 security framework implementation
- **Accessibility**: Web Content Accessibility Guidelines (WCAG) 2.1

